Currently under development

V0.1:

Patching tool accepts patchs in IPS format, checks for some consistency and applies the patch.
Currently, the patcher doesn't create IPS format patches yet. To be implemented later. It was
tested only on Ubuntu 16.04 x64, support for other OS will be added later.